          "settings": {
            "username": "Hendri H.",
            "badge_text": "Verified review",
            "date": "10/20/25",
            "heading": "Loveeeeeeeeee",
            "text": "<p>Easy to use and made my skin is smoother. I'm on my second treatment now, and I can just see the result going to be amazaaaaiiiiiingggg...... I bought the 6months bundle and loving it so far... so worth it</p>",
            "sub_text": "<p><strong>Skin Type:</strong> Combination</p><p><strong>Skin Concerns:</strong> Fine Lines and Wrinkles</p>"
          }
        },
        "review_pMfEmq": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "username": "Alexia N.",
            "badge_text": "Verified review",
            "date": "10/20/25",
            "heading": "Love it!",
            "text": "<p>I did microneedling in a practice, I liked the results but I found it expensive and it's recommended to do several sessions (with intervals). So when I found Qure and read the good reviews I decided to try it. I used it 3 times and I can really see an improvement with my skin! I think it looks overall better, glowing more and plumpier as well. I really make an experience out of it as it needs to be done properly, it's nice to take care of yourself and take your time doing it. I'm glad I bought the micro-infusion kit and I recommend it!</p>",
            "sub_text": ""
          }
        },
        "review_collapsed_aWAUyY": {
          "type": "review_collapsed",
          "settings": {
            "username": "Kerry M.",
            "badge_text": "Verified review",
            "date": "10/16/25",
            "heading": "This is amazing",
            "text": "<p>Really noticed a decrease in my wrinkles especially on my forehead. Will definitely continue to use this produc</p>",
            "sub_text": "<p><strong>Skin Type:</strong> Normal</p><p><strong>Skin Concerns:</strong> Fine Lines and Wrinkles</p>"
          }
        },
        "review_collapsed_KqYAAa": {
          "type": "review_collapsed",
          "settings": {
            "username": "Katerina G.",
            "badge_text": "Verified review",
            "date": "10/10/25",
            "heading": "So simple to use!",
            "text": "<p>Firstly the presentation of the product is exceptional - on opening the box everything is beautifully set-out. I absolutely enjoyed using the micro-infusion system - the explanation how to use was very concise and simple and I certainly believe that a few days after my skin was looking much better than before using the product.</p>",
            "sub_text": "<p><strong>Skin Type:</strong> Normal</p><p><strong>Skin Concerns:</strong> Fine Lines and Wrinkles, Dark Spots and Uneven Skin Tone</p>"
          }
        },
